les & Easy to Play<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intelligent scoreboard helps you optimize combinations and check scores at any time.</li></ul>Rolling the Dice now!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072620/extras/b62722c8383387a590b00a16f16fe81e.poster.avif?t=1733124523\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072620/extras/b62722c8383387a590b00a16f16fe81e.webm?t=1733124523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072620/extras/b62722c8383387a590b00a16f16fe81e.mp4?t=1733124523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
